summary: Performing Pianist with a demonstrated history of working in education. Experience as a soloist, chamber musician, ensemble and orchestra member. Gave concerts throughout The Netherlands, France, Switzerland, USA, Canada, India, Argentina etc. Duo partner of Sebastiaan Kemner (trombone) and James Oesi (double bass). Currently teaching in a.o. Bhutan.
